1103
01:03:20,033 --> 01:03:23,186
I wanted to drink to
celebrate today.

1104
01:03:23,266 --> 01:03:25,520
Today's the day
we told anyone about

1105
01:03:25,600 --> 01:03:27,800
our relationship.

1106
01:03:29,733 --> 01:03:32,386
But… Will it really be okay?

1107
01:03:32,466 --> 01:03:34,953
Because of me, you…

1108
01:03:35,033 --> 01:03:36,720
Mr. Kwon.

1109
01:03:36,800 --> 01:03:41,633
Do you know the words
you say to me the most?

1110
01:03:42,866 --> 01:03:44,753
"Are you okay?"

1111
01:03:44,833 --> 01:03:47,286
You always ask me,

1112
01:03:47,366 --> 01:03:50,320
if I'm really okay.

1113
01:03:50,400 --> 01:03:54,220
And suddenly,
it occurred to me today.

1114
01:03:54,300 --> 01:03:57,133
You're always asking me
whether I'm okay,

1115
01:03:58,533 --> 01:04:00,800
but what about you?

1116
01:04:02,033 --> 01:04:04,353
What if you had
no time to worry about yourself,

1117
01:04:04,433 --> 01:04:07,866
because you're always
worrying about me instead?

1118
01:04:09,700 --> 01:04:11,920
If you're not okay, Mr. Kwon,

1119
01:04:12,000 --> 01:04:13,833
then I'm not okay.

1120
01:04:15,133 --> 01:04:17,353
Because the way you feel is

1121
01:04:17,433 --> 01:04:19,833
how I feel.

1122
01:04:22,366 --> 01:04:24,053
Oh, and one more thing.

1123
01:04:24,133 --> 01:04:28,186
I wanted to see you today to
tell you this.

1124
01:04:28,266 --> 01:04:29,333
What is it?

1125
01:04:31,966 --> 01:04:33,820
That kiss scene just now…

1126
01:04:33,900 --> 01:04:35,753
We weren't kissing for real.

1127
01:04:35,833 --> 01:04:37,386
Yes, well…

1128
01:04:37,466 --> 01:04:39,120
You don't have to
bring that up anymore.

1129
01:04:39,200 --> 01:04:41,053
Don't try to avoid the subject.

1130
01:04:41,133 --> 01:04:43,820
That's just acting. Acting!

1131
01:04:43,900 --> 01:04:46,820
